name: Stone Headpiece
description:
These are made to order. Please refer to the "About" tab on the home page to find out details of how Ray Made works. 

This can be made with a gold or silver chain. YOU choose what stone you would like for the center of the headpiece. Place your order and then we will contact you within 24 hours to ask what stone and chain you would like. 

*The pictures are examples of a amethyst and onyx stone. 
Stone shapes and styles may vary depending on what you request.
